<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Medium 라벨</title>
    <style>
      @page {
        size: 80mm 60mm;
        margin: 0;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Nanum Gothic', sans-serif;
        height: 100%;
      }
      .label-content {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1, h2, p {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      /* Medium 라벨 스타일 */
      .label-medium {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        height: 100%;
        padding: 8px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        text-align: left;
      }
      
      .medium-header {
        font-size: 14pt;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      
      .medium-info {
        font-size: 8pt;
        line-height: 1.4;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="label-content">
      <div class="label-medium">
        <h2 class="medium-header"><%= productName %></h2>
        <p class="medium-info">
          등록번호: 제IIIRAX0009호 / 제품명: 댕치킨<br />
          종류 및 현태: 단미사료 / 혼합성-혼합제 / 큐브<br />
          성분량: 조단백질 36% 이상
        </p>
        <p class="medium-info">제조일자: <%= manufactureDate %></p>
        <p class="medium-info">유통기한: <%= expiryDate %></p>
        <p class="medium-info">제품수량: 1개</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

